<task><p>Approximately how many filters should Envirogreen produce for the average cost to be $75?</p></task>

<task><p>What happens to the average cost per filter as <m>x</m> increases?</p>

<p>As <m>x</m> increases, the average cost appears to be approaching a limiting value. What is that value?</p></task>

<task><p>A market analysis concludes that Envirogreen can sell 1250 filters this year. How much should they charge for one filter if they would like to make a total profit of $100,000? Use the formula:</p>  
